Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:29.49,oped,,0,0,0,,你是否满意？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:31.83,oped,,0,0,0,,睁开眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.24,oped,,0,0,0,,就能看到光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:36.71,oped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,579)}跨越这条新界线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:47.55,oped,,0,0,0,,被击倒在地 不住地叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:51.76,oped,,0,0,0,,不断抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:56.52,oped,,0,0,0,,遥远的光芒 穿透黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:01.06,oped,,0,0,0,,那是心怀信念之人的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:06.03,oped,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get low！Hey! 咆哮吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:10.53,oped,,0,0,0,,现在就行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:15.62,oped,,0,0,0,,Hey！你定会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.46,oped,,0,0,0,,苍穹之Exodus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:21.83,oped,,0,0,0,,将那残存的梦想higher
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.34,oped,,0,0,0,,不想再失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:27.09,oped,,0,0,0,,决不听信liar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:30.13,oped,,0,0,0,,期待着 yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:34.01,oped,,0,0,0,,直至死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.39,oped,,0,0,0,,壁垒越高 则越发desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:38.77,oped,,0,0,0,,向敞开的心扉中messiah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.31,oped,,0,0,0,,想要抓住变迁的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:44.77,oped,,0,0,0,,决不放弃 yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:49.40,oped,,0,0,0,,超越那被囚禁的黑夜
